{"tid":34422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我綺禮覺得時事台呢班人有好多都係狗黎","createTime":"2016-12-11T12:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T13:44:30.000Z","uid":6327,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"209a794c0ac71bef565d43ca4e17d70812a98264","tid":34422,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"冇講錯你地啊 有好多都係狗黎<br />\n有偽民主鬥士既走狗 有批鬥人既狗<br />\n熱狗青狗呢d不在話下啦<br />\n有唔理乜撚野都反既狗 <br />\n仲有一班剛剛學曉上討論區既新連登狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要反共 冇問題 我都好贊同你地<br />\n但係可唔可以唔好咁冇腦<br />\n唔講仲以為睇緊教科書入面講既文革 <br />\n講漏左一種狗 你老母食屎狗<br />\n要反要批鬥哩翻入狗竇時事台啦<br />\n走去人地台把撚啊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C18007z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC18007z.jpg&h=97f5fbc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10b634e689c21d6c29c911ad79c61256ab0787fb","tid":34422,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:03:54.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ab590e2fbc2e08511d6f6bbe93f99da773cbc5ab","tid":34422,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"樓主唔好搶我光環啦"},{"pid":"e4244cbec1450ad6161afe3454a2d16a22cd1fca","tid":34422,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16594ab4f1a7a4614f72d70daacfbb03489f19d7","tid":34422,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主唔好搶我光環啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做野唔洗你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c30992d3df3d7c1fabfa5a0029db191e308d45","tid":34422,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"ea07f4dfb9ce4b6628282524026dd8b2724d7e89","tid":34422,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11